Class HashMapStorageLayer

java.lang.Object
vrielynckpieterjan.masterproef.storagelayer.map.HashMapStorageLayer
All Implemented Interfaces:
StorageLayer
public class HashMapStorageLayer
extends java.lang.Object
implements StorageLayer
Class representing a HashMap implementation of the StorageLayer interface.
"Implementation Requirements:"
The decision was made to implement the StorageLayer with a HashMap, since the used Kademlia library could not support the size of the Attestation instances. Since the multi-value DHT is considered a building block for this thesis, the decision was made to just replace it with a HashMap. TODO: maybe try to fix this?
